{"tid":171193,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"汽車虛擬實境呢個諗頭掂唔掂","createTime":"2017-03-25T07:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T07:25:02.000Z","uid":27273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3c3f9b8df0d433e2f3fa2618219f78e39093e0","tid":171193,"uid":27273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"假設你揸緊車去緊你唔熟嘅地方你就要睇GPS<br />\n<br />\n或者聽幾多米轉左幾多米轉右.<br />\n<br />\n即係你未必可以專心揸車因為要接收或者瀏覽資訊.<br />\n<br />\n而家虛擬實境科技都發展得幾好,<br />\n<br />\n利用虛擬實境作導航應該方便過時不時望下有冇行錯.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Y5VmJ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Y5VmJ5.png&h=3740a6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過問題就嚟啦, <br />\n<br />\n個啲虛擬實境裝置應該裝喺邊度? <br />\n<br />\n如果萬一真係整咗咁架車嘅價錢又會係幾貴呢?<br />\n<br />\n利申:純粹FF"},{"pid":"2863f3133008a1cd204339731c411566b3cc989c","tid":171193,"uid":48262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"VR"},{"pid":"0453651dbc34d4483cc5ef567b60cff9e7cf90c8","tid":171193,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"唔識路就咪揸車啦"},{"pid":"d940099951ac627d21cfd26b578486705baba6c3","tid":171193,"uid":85655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"去玩灣岸啦屌"},{"pid":"9a4acb0bb5feb9890c64faeaa1eda02573ac2391","tid":171193,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"泊低係路邊用腳行一次囉"},{"pid":"a7273c5f77e2bf1223533b6fa852e7053227ea77","tid":171193,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識路就咪揸車啦</blockquote><br />\n咪臭係，香港d路有幾難認"}]}